parameters.name: Description
parameters.description: The description. The description can be up to 50 characters long.

parameters.name: Id
parameters.description: The ID of the configuration set. This parameter is required.

parameters.name: IpPoolId
parameters.description: The ID of the associated IP pool. This parameter is optional.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The name of the configuration. This parameter is required. The name must be unique and can be up to 50 characters long.
